ss as the client desired final editorial and content control enabled by the built-in CMS.</p>\n<p>One important design consideration was to use a theme that looked good on mobile and desktop, but also preserved the content layout. Considering the client wanted to manage their own content after development, an easy to use graphical system was chosen: Elementor.</p>\n<p>Some content was made to stand out by using a card-like system.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 700px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c36f66e04d32b70d4b49e5f338203701/764d0/Thyroidweek_Card_Layout.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.57142857142857%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Card layout\"\n        title=\"Card layout\"\n        src=\"/static/c36f66e04d32b70d4b49e5f338203701/8c557/Thyroidweek_Card_Layout.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c36f66e04d32b70d4b49e5f338203701/4edbd/Thyroidweek_Card_Layout.png 175w,\n/static/c36f66e04d32b70d4b49e5f338203701/13ae7/Thyroidweek_Card_Layout.png 350w,\n/static/c36f66e04d32b70d4b49e5f338203701/8c557/Thyroidweek_Card_Layout.png 700w,\n/static/c36f66e04d32b70d4b49e5f338203701/e996b/Thyroidweek_Card_Layout.png 1050w,\n/static/c36f66e04d32b70d4b49e5f338203701/2cefc/Thyroidweek_Card_Layout.png 1400w,\n/static/c36f66e04d32b70d4b49e5f338203701/764d0/Thyroidweek_Card_Layout.png 1898w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n   